                    <p>The Department of Guru Nanak Hospital, Mumbai provides diagnosis, treatment and rehabilitation for adults and children with rheumatic and related disorders. Chronic diseases like rheumatoid arthritis, osteoarthritis, gout, pseudogout and fibromyalgia are some of the diseases commonly treated.</p>
                    <p>The consultants also use different modes of therapy like pain medications, anti-inflammatory medications, chemotherapeutic agents and intra-articular steroids.</p>
